item.title: Zootopia
item.description: This is my first Adobe Indesign practice: a magazine design which is inspired by my trip in the zoo at Vietnam during reading week. Target Children are always curious about animals and treat them as friends. This magazine design aims at attracting children with cute animal silhouttes and rich colors.
